arguments.template:
<sky-alert
  [alertType]="alertType"
  [closeable]="closeable"
  [closed]="closed">
  This is a sample alert.
</sky-alert>
<select [(ngModel)]="alertType">
  <option value="info">info</option>
  <option value="success">success</option>
  <option value="warning">warning</option>
  <option value="danger">danger</option>
</select>
<sky-checkbox [(ngModel)]="closeable">
  <sky-checkbox-label>Closeable</sky-checkbox-label>
</sky-checkbox>
